        <updateDate>2020-01-23T17:17:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Safe Water for Military Families Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Defense (DOD) to ensure that, no later than January 1, 2029, it uses only non-fluorinated firefighting foam, which does not contain a perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substance (PFAS) with at least one fully fluorinated carbon atom.</p> <p>DOD shall study best practices to clean up ground contaminated by PFAS substances.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
